# Environment Configuration

## Current Setup

- `.env` - **PRODUCTION** (Monad Testnet, real users)
- `.env.testnet` - Backup of testnet deployment
- `.env.example` - Template

## What's Shared Between Testnet & Mainnet

✅ **Same (no changes needed):**
```bash
# Economic config
KAWAI_RATE_PER_MILLION
COST_RATE_PER_MILLION

# Cloudflare account
CF_ACCOUNT_ID
CF_API_TOKEN

# API keys (same for both)
ETHERSCAN_API_KEYS
OPENROUTER_API_KEYS
ZAI_API_KEYS
GEMINI_API_KEYS

# Treasury addresses (same wallets)
TREASURY_ADDRESSES

# Telegram (same bot)
TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN
TELEGRAM_CHAT_ID
```

## What's Different Between Testnet & Mainnet

❌ **Different (must change):**
```bash
# RPC URL
MONAD_RPC_URL  # testnet vs mainnet

# Contract addresses (all different after redeploy)
USDT_TOKEN_ADDRESS  # MockUSDT vs real USDT
TOKEN_ADDRESS
ESCROW_ADDRESS
PAYMENT_VAULT_ADDRESS
KAWAI_DISTRIBUTOR_ADDRESS
USDT_DISTRIBUTOR_ADDRESS
MINING_DISTRIBUTOR_ADDRESS
CASHBACK_DISTRIBUTOR_ADDRESS
REFERRAL_DISTRIBUTOR_ADDRESS

# Admin wallet (use hardware wallet for mainnet!)
ADMIN_ADDRESS

# KV namespaces (separate data)
CF_KV_CONTRIBUTORS_NAMESPACE_ID
CF_KV_USERS_NAMESPACE_ID
CF_KV_PROOFS_NAMESPACE_ID
CF_KV_SETTLEMENTS_NAMESPACE_ID
CF_KV_APIKEY_NAMESPACE_ID
CF_KV_AUTHZ_NAMESPACE_ID
CF_KV_P2PMARKETPLACE_NAMESPACE_ID
CF_KV_CASHBACK_NAMESPACE_ID
CF_KV_REVENUE_NAMESPACE_ID
CF_KV_HOLDER_NAMESPACE_ID
```

## Migration Checklist

When moving to mainnet:
- [ ] Update `MONAD_RPC_URL`
- [ ] Deploy all contracts (get new addresses)
- [ ] Update all contract addresses in `.env`
- [ ] Create fresh KV namespaces (10 namespaces)
- [ ] Update KV namespace IDs in `.env`
- [ ] Use hardware wallet for `ADMIN_ADDRESS`
- [ ] Get real USDT address
- [ ] Run `go run cmd/obfuscator-gen/main.go`

## Current Status

🟡 **Production on Testnet**
- Using testnet RPC and addresses
- Real users, but tokens have no real value
- Waiting for Monad Mainnet launch

See `DEPLOYMENT_MAINNET.md` for full migration guide.
